@AspNetCoreApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5116

### Test the Root Endpoint
Get {{AspNetCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts

### Test the JSON Status Endpoint
Get {{AspNetCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/3

### Create a brand new account
POST {{AspNetCoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "accountHolder": "Budi Santoso"
}
